body:
Yes, there should be libneuralnetworks.so that handles CPU fallback mentioned in NNAPI [doc](https://developer.android.com/ndk/guides/neuralnetworks/) and other NNAPI runtime stuff. For user-level code of NNAPI in Android 8.1, see 
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/ml/+/oreo-mr1-release
